title: Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series
text:
> Top News Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series New York Mets' Daniel Murphy celebrates after Game 4 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Chicago. The Mets won 8-3 to advance to the World Series. (AP Photo/David J. Phillip) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
